                        <li><p>reveal additional side effects, serious and unexpected adverse effects, and/ or drug interactions </p></li>
                    </ul>

                    <p>Serving as an adjunct to the continuing clinical studies and testing, Esco Pharma provides specialist services, equipment packages, and process solutions from our core platform products. This leads to improved protection of operators, reduction of cross-contamination; thereby, directly and indirectly advancing occupational health and human healthcare. </p>

