                <p><strong>References:</strong></p>
                <ol class="break-word font-80 ">
                    <li>Bonheim, M., Burns, G., Hoffer, G., Keys, D., Kovalenko, V., Maitland, A., Marks, W., Marotta, A., McMahon, N., Specht, S., Stuart, S., Yao, M., Losman, D., Moss, K., & Topic, G. (2003). <em>Electronics Industry Study Report: Semiconductors and Defense Electronics</em>. The Industrial College of the Armed Forces. Retrieved from: https://apps.dtic.mil/dtic/tr/fulltext/u2/a524792.pdf </li>
