                                    <li>Size 0 is usually the largest capsule size used orally for humans</li>
                                    <li>Size 000 are sometimes used to encapsulate the medication for rectal or vaginal use.</li>
                                    <li>The capsule should be moistened with lubricating jelly or water before insertion</li>
