                                            <li>
                                                <p>By direct hydrating the inorganic material in water.</p>
                                                <p>AI<sub>2</sub>O<sub>3</sub> + H<sub>2</sub>O &#10132; AI(OH)<sub>3</sub>
                                            </p> <strong>Examples:</strong> Aluminum Hydroxide Gel; Alugel; Amphogel; Ce-lu-gel; Cremalin; Hydroxal; Vanogel; Aluminum Phosphate Gel (Phosphagel) - Antacid
