                            <p>These solutions are intended to bathe or wash wounds surgical incisions or body tissues.</p>

                            <em>Examples are:</em>
                            <div class="rows">
                            <ul class="list-circle">
                                <li>Sterile Water for Irrigation, USP</li>
                                <li>Acetic acid for irrigation</li>
                                <li>Sodium chloride irrigation</li>
