                        <div class="card-block p-3 p-sm-4">
                            <div class="rows">
                            <div class="col s7">
                            <p><strong>Shampoo</strong> is a common hair care product used for the removal of oils, dirt, skin particles, environmental pollutants and other contaminant particles that gradually build up in hair.</p>
                            <p>The goal is <strong>to remove the unwanted build-up</strong> without stripping out so much as to make hair unmanageable.</p>
