                    <div id="Ampoules" class="collapse show" role="tabpanel" aria-labelledby="accordionHeadingOne" aria-expanded="false" data-parent="accordion">
                        <div class="card-block p-3 p-sm-4">

                            <p><strong>Ampoule</strong> - A container sealed by fusion and to be opened exclusively by breaking. The contents are intended for use on one occasion only.</p>
                            <div class="col s3">
                                <img style="display: block; margin: 0 auto; width: 219px;" src="/images/upload/ampoule.jpg" class="img-responsive">
                            </div>
                            <p>Important Characteristics of Glass as an Adequate Material for Drugs</p>
                            <table style="margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;" border="1" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" class="table table-bordered">
                                <tbody>
                                    <tr>
                                        <td valign="top" width="312">
                                            <p><strong>Characteristics</strong>
                                            </p>
                                        </td>
                                        <td valign="top" width="312">
                                            <p><strong>Importance</strong>
                                            </p>
                                        </td>
                                    </tr>
                                    <tr>
                                        <td valign="top" width="312">
                                            <p>They can filter specific wave lengths</p>
                                        </td>
                                        <td valign="top" width="312">
                                            <p>Packaging of photosensitive substances</p>
                                        </td>
