                                    <tr>
                                        <td valign="top" width="312">
                                            <p>High fusion point</p>
                                        </td>
                                        <td valign="top" width="312">
                                            <p>It tolerates the sterilization process (by vapor at 1,210°C, and dry at 2,600°C) – microbiologic control.</p>
                                        </td>
                                    </tr>
                                    <tr>
                                        <td valign="top" width="312">
                                            <p>Excellent chemical resistance</p>
