            'details' => 'There are numerous factors that must be considered when deciding which primary packaging container to utilize. Ensure that the drug and its route of administration must be compatible with the container of choice.',
            'content' => '
            <div id="accordion" class="solution_accordion w-100" role="tablist" aria-multiselectable="true">


                <div class="mb-3">
                    <div role="tab">
                        <div class="accordion-head px-2 py-2">
