                  <li>Khan Academy. (n.d.). <em>Biotechnology: Gel Electrophoresis</em>. Retrieved from: https://www.khanacademy.org/science/ap-biology/gene-expression-and-regulation/biotechnology/a/gel-electrophoresis  </li>
                  <li>Kozlowski, L. (2017). Proteome-pI: proteome isoelectric point database. <em>Nucleic Acids Research</em>. doi: 10.1093/nar/gkw978  </li>
