                    <li>Batch or lot number as per the manufacturer.</li>

                    <li>Total volume of preparations in solution.</li>

                    <li>Any special storage requirements.</li>

                    <li>Name and concentration of any added antimicrobial preservatives, if any. If none, then information that no antimicrobial preservative is in the preparation should be present.</li>
